largest health impacts

154
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:31,816
and the worst consequences 
for climate change.

155
00:08:31,817 --> 00:08:35,199
A 2019 analysis concluded 
that as a consequence,

156
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,081
the nuclear phase-out has led to

157
00:08:37,082 --> 00:08:40,599
1,100 avoidable deaths 
per year in Germany

158
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:44,399
due to the increased air pollution 
in the years after 2010.

159
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:49,899
So, in conclusion, nuclear energy feels 
way more dangerous than it actually is.

160
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,466
No matter how you look at it,

161
00:08:51,467 --> 00:08:54,766
